OL,3,CPlea to re-open murder case against
OL,4,Chusband after judge ruled he killed
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FThe family of a wealthy heiress say
OL,8,Fthey want police to reopen the murder
OL,9,Fcase against her husband after a judge
OL,10,Fruled he had unlawfully killed his
OL,11,Fwife.
OL,13,FDonald McPherson, 51, was ordered to
OL,14,Fbe found not guilty of the 2017 murder
OL,15,Fof Paula Leeson, 47, on a judge's
OL,16,Fdirection to the jury halfway through
OL,17,Fhis trial in 2021.
