OL,3,CPlea to re-open murder case against
OL,4,Chusband after judge ruled he killed
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FBut Ms Leeson's family successfully
OL,8,Fblocked his bid to inherit her #4.4
OL,9,Fmillion estate by bringing legal
OL,10,Fproceedings against McPherson at
OL,11,FManchester Civil Courts of Justice.
OL,13,FMr Justice Richard Smith emphatically
OL,14,Fruled McPherson had unlawfully killed
OL,15,Fhis wife by compressing her neck in an
OL,16,Farm lock then putting her in a
OL,17,Fswimming pool leaving her to drown.
OL,19,FGiving his ruling he said: "Don's
OL,20,Fmotive for unlawfully killing Paula
OL,21,FLeeson is clear: money."
