OL,7,FFollowing the ruling Ms Leeson's
OL,8,Fheartbroken family now say they will
OL,9,Fnot rest until "serial liar" McPherson
OL,10,Fis back behind bars.
OL,12,FMcPherson was not present or
OL,13,Frepresented in court and is believed
OL,14,Fto be living somewhere in the South
OL,15,FPacific.
