OL,7,FMs Leeson oversaw the skip hire part
OL,8,Fof her family's successful civil
OL,9,Fengineering business that her father,
OL,10,FWilly, 80, had built up in Sale,
OL,11,FGreater Manchester, after emigrating
OL,12,Ffrom County Wicklow, Ireland, in the
OL,13,F1960s.
OL,15,FMs Leeson, a mother-of-one, and her
OL,16,Fbrother, Neville, stood to inherit the
OL,17,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
