OL,4,Chusband after judge ruled he killed
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FOutside court, the Leeson family said
OL,8,Fthe ruling confirmed what they had
OL,9,Fknown all along: that Donald McPherson
OL,10,Fkilled Paula.
OL,12,F"Today is bittersweet. It has been
OL,13,Fvery difficult for us to hear this
OL,14,Foutcome without it being followed by
OL,15,Fthe sentencing of Donald McPherson to
OL,16,Fprison," their statement said.
