OL,3,CPlea to re-open murder case against
OL,4,Chusband after judge ruled he killed
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,F"This was a pre-meditated, cold-
OL,8,Fblooded murder, entirely motivated by
OL,9,FDonald McPherson's wicked greed, to
OL,10,Fseek to benefit from insurance
OL,11,Fpolicies totalling #3.9 million, the
OL,12,Fmajority of which he had incepted
OL,13,Fdishonestly, deceptively and without
OL,14,FPaula's knowledge."
OL,16,FMcPherson had taken out multiple
OL,17,Fsecret life insurance policies on his
OL,18,Fwife before her death, worth #3.5
OL,19,Fmillion alone.
