OL,4,Chusband after judge ruled he killed
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FMs Leeson, who was 5ft 5in, drowned in
OL,8,Fthe pool that was less than 4ft deep,
OL,9,Fthough she could swim and was an
OL,10,Fotherwise healthy mother of one.
OL,12,FLawyers for the Leeson family argue
OL,13,Fthat to save herself from drowning she
OL,14,Fcould simply have stood up, so must
OL,15,Fhave been choked before being put into
OL,16,Fthe water unconscious.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
