OL,4,Chusband after judge ruled he killed
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FMr McPherson told police he awoke to
OL,8,Ffind Ms Leeson face down in the
OL,9,Fshallow swimming pool at a holiday
OL,10,Fcottage in remote western Denmark he
OL,11,Fhad booked for the couple, on 6 June
OL,12,F2017.
OL,14,FHer death was initially treated as a
OL,15,Ftragic accident by the Danish
OL,16,Fauthorities ` though she had suffered
OL,17,F13 separate external injuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
