OL,4,Chusband after judge ruled he killed
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FWithin hours Mr McPherson was
OL,8,Ftransferring thousands of pounds from
OL,9,Fher accounts to cover his debts, the
OL,10,Fcourt heard.
OL,12,FHe had also "systematically" deleted
OL,13,Fdata from his wife's phone which may
OL,14,Fhave explained what happened and
OL,15,Frefused to give police access to his
OL,16,Fown phone.
