OL,3,CPlea to re-open murder case against
OL,4,Chusband after judge ruled he killed
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FSoon after, Mr McPherson cleared their
OL,8,Fhome in Sale of his late wife's
OL,9,Fpossessions and joined a bereavement
OL,10,Fgroup, Widowed And Young ` that he
OL,11,Fcalled "Tinder for widows."
OL,13,FHe was later arrested in the UK as
OL,14,Fpolice looked into his financial
OL,15,Fbackground.
OL,17,FMr McPherson has always denied any
OL,18,Finvolvement in his wife's death and
OL,19,Fafter he was acquitted of murder, in a
OL,20,Fstatement through his solicitors, he
OL,21,Fdescribed it as a "tragic accident".
