OL,7,FThe family called on Greater
OL,8,FManchester Police and the Crown
OL,9,FProsecution Service to re-open the
OL,10,Fmurder investigation.
OL,12,FThey added: "As the judgement
OL,13,Fdemonstrates, Donald McPherson is an
OL,14,Fevil, dangerous man and a long-
OL,15,Fstanding fraudster. He has convictions
OL,16,Fworldwide for dishonesty offences.
