OL,7,F"We hope the judgment also serves as a
OL,8,Fwarning to all who unwisely chose to
OL,9,Fassociate with Donald McPherson or
OL,10,Fwhatever he may now call himself. He
OL,11,Fis an extremely dangerous individual."
OL,13,FThe family said they will not rest
OL,14,Funtil McPherson is behind bars for
OL,15,Fkilling their loved one.
